title: General comments
description: Any general comments the coder wants to add about this study

title: Country
description: Country (or countries) where the data were collected

title: Methods
description: Description of the methods used by the study

title: Sample size
description: Total number of human participants in the study (note: the actual sample size may be larger if multiple observations are collected per participant)

title: Logic model
description: Description of the main elements in the intervention logic model (i.e. the logic model of the problem and the logic model of change)

title: Target group(s)
description: Description of the target group(s) of the intervention

title: Determinant(s)
description: Description of the determinant(s) the intervention targets

title: Problem
description: Description of the problem and the background of the problem

title: Method(s)
description: Description of the method(s) employed to target the determinant(s)

title: Application(s)
description: Description of the application(s) in which the method(s) are implemented
